{
  "chapter": 24,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十四回七情魔。白服公子章痴闯入呼哈娜帐幕欲陪睡，与芮玮、呼哈娜三人言语交锋，章痴痴迷于情，直言芮玮不爱呼哈娜便是傻子。黑服公子葛恨来寻，称大哥有事相商，临走嘲讽呼哈娜难看，呼哈娜气哭。芮玮夜间恢复体力，次晨告别呼哈娜，呼哈娜赠伊吾国通行信符，嘱其小心原氏兄弟催眠术。芮玮赴金山寻野儿，遇七情魔（喜魔温笑、怒魔吴愤、哀魔莫悲、惧魔黄衣公子、爱魔章痴、恶魔葛恨、欲魔赵柔），灰衣公子莫悲以\"芮玮吾儿\"之计引芮玮前来，乃受一灯神尼所托传话。紫衣公子吴愤与芮玮交手被玄妙三十掌擒住。原氏兄弟（原思聪、原思敏）出现，双方开战。七情魔创圆阵合力，六人功力贯注温笑一人，催眠术对六魔失效，唯温笑闭目防御。原思聪施计拖延，暗中以乐声惑温笑。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_zhang_chi",
      "text": "喂！喂！那不是给你睡的？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_chi",
      "speaker_name": "章痴",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "不是给我睡，给谁睡的？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_zhang_chi",
      "text": "是给他睡的，你快出去！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_chi",
      "speaker_name": "章痴",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "但他不愿跟你睡，徒呼奈何？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮公子，你当真不愿睡在这帐内？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhang_chi",
      "text": "阁下怎知我不愿睡在这帐内？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_chi",
      "speaker_name": "章痴",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "章某耳朵不聋，适才明明听到有个傻小子说要在帐外坐一夜，敢情是听错了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhang_chi",
      "text": "阁下是听错了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_chi",
      "speaker_name": "章痴",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "可惜不叫我睡，却叫这傻子睡，人家傻子直心眼，不爱睡在这里又有何用！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhang_chi",
      "text": "阁下左一声傻子右一声傻子，骂的是谁？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_chi",
      "speaker_name": "章痴",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不是傻子谁是傻子？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_zhang_chi",
      "text": "芮公子才不是傻子，只有你看来像个痴子。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_chi",
      "speaker_name": "章痴",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "世间男儿难得痴，我的名字叫章痴，就是个痴子又何妨？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhang_chi",
      "text": "阁下名字叫章痴，芮某的名字却不是叫芮傻，阁下自称痴子，在下却不是傻子！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_chi",
      "speaker_name": "章痴",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你还不自认傻子，这样漂亮的女子在眼前你不爱，我要爱还来不及，怎说不是个傻子？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhang_chi",
      "text": "倘若有个更漂亮的女子在这里呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_chi",
      "speaker_name": "章痴",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "还有个更漂亮的女子，在哪里？在那里？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhang_chi",
      "text": "我是比方说，阁下别听错了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_chi",
      "speaker_name": "章痴",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "真有这么个女子，我更要爱她。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhang_chi",
      "text": "倘若有一打漂亮女子在这里呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_chi",
      "speaker_name": "章痴",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "真有的话，我全爱！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhang_chi",
      "text": "果真是个痴子！你快出去吧！莫要在此再胡言乱语，冒渎玉人，要知她是伊吾国公主，并非常人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_chi",
      "speaker_name": "章痴",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "公主、常人有何两样，你要爱她，管她是公主还是常人，否则她就悲哀了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_zhang_chi",
      "text": "章痴，你还不走，我要叫人赶你了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_chi",
      "speaker_name": "章痴",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "我本要走的，现在不走了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_zhang_chi",
      "text": "你……你为什么不走？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_chi",
      "speaker_name": "章痴",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我要问那个傻子是不是真的爱你，若不是的话，我再也不走了。你爱不爱她？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_chi",
      "speaker_name": "章痴",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你既否认不在帐外坐一夜，便是要在帐内睡，既睡在这里，自然你是真心爱她的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮公子……你……快回答他的话……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_hen",
      "speaker_name": "黑服公子",
      "listener": "char_zhang_chi",
      "text": "五哥，难怪半天找不到，原来又被狐狸精迷住！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_chi",
      "speaker_name": "章痴",
      "listener": "char_ge_hen",
      "text": "原来是六弟，你回去向大哥说，我明天自会与大伙相见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_hen",
      "speaker_name": "葛恨",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "这异族女子一点也不好看，五哥为何被她迷住，大哥说有事相商，还是快回去。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_ge_hen",
      "text": "滚出去！滚出去！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_chi",
      "speaker_name": "章痴",
      "listener": "char_ge_hen",
      "text": "六弟，我们走罢！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_hen",
      "speaker_name": "葛恨",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "这一生气，更是难看！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao",
      "speaker_name": "小桃",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "公子要走了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao",
      "text": "突厥兵可是撤离了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "我要走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao",
      "speaker_name": "小桃",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "是芮公子欺侮公主？你好大胆子……敢对我们公主无礼！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao",
      "text": "别胡说，我……可没有欺侮你们公主。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你当真要走？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "我体力恢复，不敢再麻烦公主。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我知道无法留你，但不知你现在要去哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "我一时不会离开金山，因有一位好友在此神秘失踪，直至找到后才回中原。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "父王也要一段时间才归国，希你有暇来此。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "好，在下这就告辞。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "且等一下。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这是伊吾国通行无阻的信符，尔后你持此到伊吾国来，无人会阻你，如遇我国两大高手魔眼摄魂原氏兄弟，他们要对你为难，就说这是我给的，他一定不敢再加刁难。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "原氏兄弟可是长得瘦长的老头？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "他兄弟俩人都通邪术，你被催眠想必是他俩人的杰作，尔后你要小心。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "我不一定能到贵国去，但对原氏兄弟实在无法抵御，只有借重此牌，在下多谢公主。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao",
      "speaker_name": "小桃",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "公子就是不能到我国来，他日也要给公主送个信，莫要一去便如陌生。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "芮玮决不会将公主忘去，两年后只要不死，不用送信，我一定到伊吾国看望公主！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那我两年后恭迎大驾。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "只怕那时，我已不在世上。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bei",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣公子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮玮吾儿，你找得老夫好像……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bei",
      "speaker_name": "莫悲",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你是何人，要拦着咱们去路，莫非知道吾儿行踪。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_chi",
      "speaker_name": "章痴",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我认识他，他名字叫芮玮！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衣公子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "阁下也姓芮。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "在下就是芮玮。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bei",
      "speaker_name": "莫悲",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "啊！你就是芮玮，可知为父找得你好苦！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_mo_bei",
      "text": "在下与你不识，说话不要辱及先父！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_yi_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黄衣公子",
      "listener": "char_mo_bei",
      "text": "三哥，你这下可闯祸了！叫你不要瞎叫，现在把主儿叫出来，看你如何收拾？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_fen",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣公子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这有什么不可收拾，他要不服气就打一架！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bei",
      "speaker_name": "莫悲",
      "listener": "char_wu_fen",
      "text": "我这样叫他是番好意，怎会打架，应该感谢我才是。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮兄，我三哥确是好意叫你，你莫要生气。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "纵然是好意，也不应该这样叫我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bei",
      "speaker_name": "莫悲",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不这样叫你，你哪会闻声匆匆直赶来，要知一灯神尼吩咐的事，咱们兄弟不得不办，而金山一带辽阔千里，如何去找你，莫某灵机一动，才思得此计找你，倒未想到果然灵验。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_mo_bei",
      "text": "一灯神尼！她老人吩咐你们什么事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_hen",
      "speaker_name": "葛恨",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "要知道，快叫三哥一声爹爹！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ge_hen",
      "text": "要说就说，不说就算，芮某可不是好欺侮的人。你若再辱及先父，在下不客气了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_fen",
      "speaker_name": "吴愤",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好小子！敢在咱们兄弟面前发狠，吃我一拳。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_chi",
      "speaker_name": "章痴",
      "listener": "char_huang_yi_gong_zi",
      "text": "四哥别丢人，这小子没什么了不起。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_yi_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黄衣公子",
      "listener": "char_zhang_chi",
      "text": "他是一灯神尼的朋友，本领一定很大，三十六计，咱们还是快逃的好！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_huang_yi_gong_zi",
      "text": "逃什么，好好站着？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮兄，请高抬贵手，放过我二弟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我二弟的脾气很坏，芮兄见谅。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "在下出手鲁莽，尚请原谅。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "咱们兄弟的性情各有怪癖，行事不免有点异常，二弟对你无礼，温某代为谢罪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "昨日咱们遇到一灯，她老人家吩咐转告芮兄一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "什么事，烦请转告？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "她老人家说……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_hen",
      "speaker_name": "葛恨",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "大哥，暂且不要告诉他。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_ge_hen",
      "text": "六弟有什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_hen",
      "speaker_name": "葛恨",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "等他胜了六弟，再说不迟！二哥不小心被你擒住，有本领再将我葛恨擒一次。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ge_hen",
      "text": "我与你无冤无仇，为何要擒你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_hen",
      "speaker_name": "葛恨",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我要打你，自然就引起仇恨！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_ge_hen",
      "text": "六弟住手，咱们来此要打的不是他，何必自费力气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "打的不是他，可是咱们兄弟？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_hen",
      "speaker_name": "葛恨",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "原氏兄弟！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "你们来得正好，免得咱们兄弟找。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "七情魔数年前已是手下败将，今日再来何足言勇。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "那年咱们兄弟败在邪术下，今天再来已非当年的七情魔，有本领在真功夫上见个真章。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "speaker_name": "原思敏",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "敢情七情魔不再怕催眠术？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_fen",
      "speaker_name": "吴愤",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "催眠术不过邪魔外道，雕虫小技，咱们兄弟怕什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_wu_fen",
      "text": "口说不怕，但今日七情魔仍要败在你们不屑的邪术下！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_hen",
      "speaker_name": "葛恨",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "胡说八道！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "speaker_name": "原思敏",
      "listener": "char_ge_hen",
      "text": "不信就试试！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "今日咱们兄弟算认栽了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "你们本就注定要失败。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 375,
      "line_end": 375
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "要是一对一，不用十招，我便可宰一个！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 379
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "也不见得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 383,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "怎么不见得，不信一个个来比，十招不败，我兄弟两人自认不敌！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 385,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "别吹大气！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 389,
      "line_end": 389
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_wu_fen",
      "text": "要是吴愤和老夫独斗，老夫确信一招可败！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 391,
      "line_end": 391
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "text": "大哥，他们怎么知道咱们来到这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 397,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "speaker_name": "原思敏",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "怪啊！咱们一向住在伊吾国，来到这里行动神秘，他们怎会知道？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 401,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "这很简单，咱们到伊吾国打听清楚你兄弟两人随国王远游，便千里追踪，你们行动虽隐秘，但伊吾国王的目标太大，不难找到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 405,
      "line_end": 407
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "千里追踪！这是一段很长的路程。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 409,
      "line_end": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "确是一段很长的路程。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 411,
      "line_end": 411
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "那你们该感到疲倦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 413,
      "line_end": 413
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "疲倦……疲倦……唔！我们都疲倦了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 415,
      "line_end": 415
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "小心催眠术！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 417,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_wu_fen",
      "text": "你大哥已累得闭下眼睛，你也该睡了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 429,
      "line_end": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_mo_bei",
      "text": "你成天中悲哀，名字却叫莫悲，岂非好笑已极，今天我给你改名莫睡，那你应该成天要睡了！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 433,
      "line_end": 437
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "催眠术果是雕虫小技！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 445,
      "line_end": 445
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "你以为凭仗此阵便不再怕催眠术？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 451,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "咱们创得此阵，早就想到贵兄弟的邪术将成废物，今日试来，果然不错！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 453,
      "line_end": 455
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "这阵道理简单，六魔功力贯注在你一人身上，就连精神也失去，是故不再怕催眠术。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 459,
      "line_end": 461
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "你们纵然知道这道理，无法破去惟有乖乖地等待失败的命运。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 463,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "你的兄弟虽不怕催眠术，但你精神还在，老夫尚可向你施术。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 467,
      "line_end": 469
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "温某想到此点，闭下目来，看你又如何对我施术？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 471,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "speaker_name": "原思敏",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "你以为闭着眼睛，便对你无可奈何？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 473,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "text": "正是无可奈何，否则温某早就中术了！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 475,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "speaker_name": "原思敏",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "但你现在要中术也不为迟！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 477,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "text": "又吹大气，小心把旁观的芮兄吹跑了，咱们还有要事对他说。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 479,
      "line_end": 481
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "究竟是什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 483,
      "line_end": 483
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "别慌！别慌！等原氏两老儿被咱们打输求饶，再说不迟。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 485,
      "line_end": 487
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "住手！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 495,
      "line_end": 495
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "如今只剩下你一人，不出十招，温某定要把你擒住，那时再擒逃出的那一人，不怕你们不一一求饶。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 499,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "五年前，咱们兄弟一时意气将你们兄弟七人打败，如今要求饶，老夫向你们求好了，我那兄弟脾气刚烈，希望放他一马。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 501,
      "line_end": 503
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "你要求饶？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 505,
      "line_end": 505
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "我无法抵御，当然是真的！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 507,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "当年你们兄弟两人将咱们一一点伤要穴，好不容易才恢复，今天你一人担下罪过，就把点伤咱们的那根指头折断好了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 509,
      "line_end": 511
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "你可是不愿意？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 513,
      "line_end": 514
    }
